# Lint code changes

After editing or adding source files in this project, always run lint before considering the work done:

```bash
yarn lint
```

- Run from the `spa-frontend` project root (`src/main/spa-frontend`).
- Fix every reported ESLint error in files you changed.
- Prefer fixing issues manually; use `yarn lint:fix` only for safe auto-fixes.
- Do not leave lint failures in your final suggestions.

If lint fails, resolve the issues and run `yarn lint` again until it passes.
